    "desc": "Powerful and Free Online Fundraising Platform for 100+ Types of Causes. Beautiful Fundraising Pages, Social Superpowers, Secure Money Withdrawal. 90% Platform Satisfaction score. Fund Any Cause That Matters: Nonprofits, Individuals, Social Enterprises, Animal Fundraisers, Art Projects, Schools, Sports and Businesses. Create your Fundraiser Now for Free!",
    "navbar": "Start\nFund anything\nHow it works\nGrow results\nAbout\nSearch",
    "text": "Help Center\n·\nBlog\nSign in\nStart\nFund anything\nHow it works\nGrow results\nAbout\nSearch\nNext Generation Crowdfunding for Positive Impact\nFundRazr platform makes crowdfunding and online fundraising easy, fast and effective. 0% platform fee.\nGet Started Free\nPowerful, Free Online Fundraising Platform\nProven, multi-purpose crowdfunding technology for effective organizational and individual fundraising\nI'm a nonprofit\nI'm an individual\nI'm a business\nSeamless online fundraising experience\nfor you and your donors\nCreate your fundraising campaign in minutes\nLaunch your state-of-the-art, mobile-friendly fundraising project equipped with complete crowdfunding functionality quickly and easily. It’s more than just a campaign - turn it into a micro-site with photos, social links and its own news feed!\nReach more people with social sharing superpowers\nWith best-in-class “one-click” sharing to Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, Messenger, WhatsApp, text and email, it’s effortless to keep your community informed and inspired to give.\nConvenient giving experience for donors\nRaising money on FundRazr is secure and easy. Donors enjoy a seamless giving experience with all the most popular and up-to-date payment tools like PayPal, Stripe (credit cards), GPay, Apple Pay and more.\nAdvanced fundraising for organizations\nWith enterprise-class online fundraising and crowdfunding capabilities, nonprofits, professional teams, and fundraisers have the powerful tools they need to run and effectively manage various types of campaigns. see more\nRated \"Excellent\" - both by users, and independent experts!\n$151+ million\nraised and counting\n179750+\nfundraising campaigns\n65%\nsatisfaction score\nlearn more\nEasily show donors their impact -\na gift is so much more than just money!\nTurn your ask into a Wishlist\nBreak down your ask into wishlist items that let supporters respond to specific needs. Working similarly to registries for weddings or baby showers, this type of ask has been proven to be more engaging and successful.\nOffer perks and thank-you gifts as a token of gratitude\nGive a perk to your supporters, like a t-shirt or signed card, in exchange for or on top of their donation.\nCelebrate your achievements and milestones\nAutomatically generated milestone graphics allow you to visually share progress with your community.\nVersatile set of engaging campaign types\nFundRazr’s traditional and innovative online fundraising and crowdfunding project types for organizations are aimed to effectively acquire, engage and retain new donors. A wide range of projects (peer-to-peer, microprojects, charity storefront, do-it-yourself projects, etc) help professional fundraisers involve their crowd into giving during the entire year.\nabout perks and wishlists\nYour success is our success.\nThat's why we are so committed to help you.\nPerfect fundraising setup\nFundRazr is flexible, operates internationally, offers multiple creative solutions for various organizational tasks and has a powerful social media toolset for promoting the campaigns.\nWe look forward to working together again!\nLorenzo Boffi\n\nraised $412,000 for cancer research\nSuccess in less than a week\nWe managed to hit our goal in less than a week! FundRazr is simple to use and I really liked its social sharing. I shared my fundraiser not only on Facebook but through email, Messenger and most important, Whatsapp where most of my network is. \nOverall, great experience. \nJennifer Lo\n\nraised $72,000 for healthcare\nThank you!\nWe use FundRazr to raise money for people who have Corgis and Corgi mixes that have high cost veterinary needs but can’t afford them. We have raised over $200,000 with the help of FundRazr for our clients!\nPaige Davis\n\nraised 200,000 for animals\n0% platform fee. Free fundraising\nour free pricing mission\nUnlimited Causes, Unlimited Impact\n100+ types of causes supported.\nWe believe that a high-quality online fundraising platform should be freely accessible to everyone.\nNonprofits and Charities\nFor professional fundraisers learn more\nPersonal\nFundraising\nFor individual fundraisers learn more\nSocial\nEnterprises\nFor-profits with a mission learn more\nCorporate Social Responsibility\nFor employee giving programs learn more\nCrowdfunding as a Service\nFor agencies and third-parties learn more\nArt and Music Crowdfunding\nFor creative teams and projects learn more\nSchool\nFundraising\nFor STEM projects and education learn more\nSports\nFundraising\nFor athletes and competitions learn more\nAnimal\nFundraising\nFor pet rescues and wildlife learn more\nFiscal\nSponsorship\nFor fiscal sponsors and their projects learn more\nGet better results with insights\ndirectly from your command center.\nCrowdfunding project performance analytics\nMake informed decisions based on real data. Track traffic, amount of donations, social media followers, and more.\nBoth live and automated platform coaching support\nWhatever you need help with, our team will get your question answered. Automated tips and coaching about best practices and performance boosters are also built right into our platform.\nTransactions and donor reports for full transparency\nTrack your donations, transactions, and donor demographic data for accountability, transparency and accurate reporting.\nAutomatic tax receipts *\nIssue customizable tax receipts to online and offline donors with a click of a button.\n* only for organizations\nTrusted by over 4,000\nleading impact organizations\nYou can do it too!\nContinue the success of our fundraising community\nRestaurants have been some of the hardest-hit businesses by COVID-19, losing nearly all of their income as they are forced to shutter their doors.\nAt the same time, our communities' frontline workers, like nurses, police officers, and paramedics, are being pushed harder than ever before. \nFeed the Frontlines Detroit has come up with an ingenious solution. They're raising money to provide essential workers with meals purchased from their local struggling restaurants! \nSo far, they've raised $107,000! \nHere's how they did it:\n  Ingenious solution that benefits two sectors in need of help\n  Community outreach through corporate partnerships\n  Providing donors with updates and progress\nGood luck!\nSince the world locked down, the needs of remote Indigenous communities have gone far beyond what government relief plans offer.\nThat's why Teara Fraser, pilot and CEO of Iskwew Air, has brought together a circle of Indigenous women to source supplies from local vendors and airlift them to remote Indigenous communities that are not getting the bare essentials that they need.\nAlready, the project has surpassed $20,000 and accomplished some amazing things - even bringing a little boy and his father back to their family.\nHere's how they did it:\n  Leveraged existing skills and resources for a cause\n  Acted on an urgent situation to serve a population in need\n  Outreach resulting in donations and media coverage\nGreat job!\nThe Nelson and District Women's Centre's programs offer food, comfort and community to women, empowering them to develop new skills and build networks of solidarity.\nBut now, the Centre is re-evaluating its priorities and facing a serious budget shortfall. Thanks to a well-run crowdfunding campaign, they have raised  $15,720 - 105% of their goal!\nHere's what this campaign did right:\n Beautiful perks for donors, like postcards illustrated by local artists\n Storytelling - we learn all about the Centre's history and mission\n Urgency - the Centre's budget shortfall means they're fundraising for an immediate need\nAmazing work!\nReady to get started?\nGet Started Free\nRequest a Demo\nCreate\nAnyone can start a FundRazr campaign for FREE.\nShare\nEasily share your campaign and reach more people.\nCollect\nReceive and access your money right away.\nGet started free\nFund anything\nNonprofit Crowdfunding\nPersonal Fundraising\nSocial Enterprise Crowdfunding\nCSR | Employee Giving Programs\nFiscal Sponsorship Crowdfunding\nSports Fundraising\nSchool Fundraising\nMusic and Arts Fundraising\nAnimal Rescue Fundraising\nExplore\nPlatform Tour\nPricing and Fees\nWhy FundRazr\nPeer-to-Peer Fundraising\nPerks and Wish lists\nDIY Fundraising\nMicroprojects Fundraising\nFundraising Widgets\nSuccess Guide | Stories\nLearn more\nAbout FundRazr\nBlog | Impact Crowdfunding\nCountries and Currencies\nDiscover Campaigns\nFAQ\nMedia Coverage\nPress Kit\nLetter of Subordination\nHelp Center | Support\nPartners\nCrowdfunding-as-a-Service\nPayPal\nStripe\nFacebook Fundraising\nOver The Edge\nPartner Sign Up\nRequest a Demo\nSpeak with a Crowdfunding Strategist\nContact Us\nFollow us!\nSupport\nTerms of Service\nPrivacy Policy\nCopyright ©2009-2023 ConnectionPoint Systems Inc. (CPSI) · FundRazr® and the FundRazr® logo are registered trademarks of CPSI.",
